                                需要睇圖
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="question">
                        <div class="question-header">
                            <span><span class="question-num">Q24</span>以下哪個立體有均勻截面？</span>
                            <span class="question-score">1分</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="question-content">
                            <strong>選項：</strong><br>
                            A. 圓柱<br>
                            B. 圓錐<br>
                            C. 四棱錐<br>
                            D. 三角稜柱
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer-section">
                            <div class="answer-label" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">📖 顯示答案 ▼</div>
                            <div class="answer-content">
                                <strong>答案：A (圓柱)</strong>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="question">
                        <div class="question-header">
                            <span><span class="question-num">Q25</span>求圖中六邊形ABCDEG的面積</span>
                            <span class="question-score">1分</span>
                        </div>
                        <img src="s1_p2_q25.png" alt="Q25 圖片" class="question-image" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                        <div class="question-content">
                            需要睇圖
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer-section">
                            <div class="answer-label" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">📖 顯示答案 ▼</div>
                            <div class="answer-content">
                                需要睇圖
