                    </div>
                    <div class="question">
                        <div class="question-header">
                            <span><span class="question-num">Q26</span>圖中為一個棱柱。求它的體積</span>
                            <span class="question-score">1分</span>
                        </div>
                        <img src="s1_p2_q26.png" alt="Q26 圖片" class="question-image" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                        <div class="question-content">
                            需要睇圖
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer-section">
                            <div class="answer-label" onclick="toggleAnswer(this)">📖 顯示答案 ▼</div>
