                    </div>
                    <div class="question">
                        <div class="question-header">
                            <span><span class="question-num">Q28</span>圖中所示為一個棱柱。</span>
                            <span class="question-score">1分</span>
                        </div>
                        <img src="s1_p2_q28.png" alt="Q28 圖片" class="question-image" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                        <div class="question-content">
                            需要睇圖
                        </div>
                        <div class="answer-section">
